snippet.title: Wildermyth: Console Edition Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Find out more: www.aurochdigital.com/wildermyth-console-edition

Wildermyth: Console Edition launches 22 October 2024 on PlayStation 4|5, Xbox One and Series X|S and Nintendo Switch.  Lead a band of unique heroes and shape their destiny in this character-driven tactical RPG. With procedural storytelling, dynamic character development, and strategic combat, Wildermyth offers endless replayability and the opportunity to create your own legendary tales.

Join our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/AurochDigital
